headline: Jetaire Group Secures Landmark Global Approvals with INVICTA the Leading Flammability Reduction Technology for Airbus and Boeing Aircraft
summary: Jetaire Group celebrates a pivotal year of global regulatory achievements expanding its leadership in aviation fuel tank safety and ignition mitigation means (IMM) technology.
